{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_14", "eventName": "慈悲燈塔", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "14-11", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "所謂“英雄”", "storyInfo": "Logos以咒術再現特雷西斯的劍術並斬下食腐者之王一臂，自己也跌落山崖。而寄託了女妖意志的作戰平台救下了Logos。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "50_g18_originiumcave", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_boneflute_low", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……喪鐘。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是……Logos先生吹響的骨哨。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "骨哨……;……為誰而響？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line18", "option2": "line18"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "阿米婭……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line24"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事的，博士。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是一下想起了……很多很多事。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前在羅德島的時候，很少見到Logos先生以女妖之主的身分自居。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他總說自己和Scout先生還有Misery先生他們沒有區別，僅是一位相信著羅德島理想的薩卡茲幹員。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以……出發的那天，當我看到Logos先生換上了王庭服飾的時候……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從他的眼睛裡，感受到了很大的決心……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有……悲哀。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "stopmusic", "attr